14:13.293 --> 14:16.162
but I've been trying
to get a job at a kitchen

14:16.196 --> 14:18.064
- at a really good restaurant, and...
- Mm-hmm.

14:18.098 --> 14:20.966
I haven't been able
to find anything yet.

14:21.001 --> 14:23.936
I was thinking that maybe

14:23.970 --> 14:25.838
you might know someone?

14:25.872 --> 14:29.375
