would be weird for me?

14:29.409 --> 14:32.712
Honey, I would do
<i>anythi</i> to help you.

14:33.714 --> 14:35.548
I wish that you felt
more comfortable...

14:35.582 --> 14:38.351
It was nothing to do
with you. I swear.

14:38.385 --> 14:41.320
I hate asking for help
from anyone,

14:41.355 --> 14:42.421
ever since I was little.

14:42.456 --> 14:44.023
You know...

14:44.057 --> 14:46.058
"The deaf kid needs help."

14:46.093 --> 14:48.761
Everyone needs help sometimes.

14:49.996 --> 14:51.731
I know,

14:51.765 --> 14:53.866
and I really want this,

14:53.900 --> 14:55.801
so I'm breaking my rule.

14:58.905 --> 15:01.874
- How you feeling?
- Fine.

15:03.610 --> 15:05.411
Your lawyer said we have
a really good shot.

15:06.446 --> 15:08.681
And I'll be there,
both the girls...

15:08.715 --> 15:11.183
- John and Kathryn if you want them.
- No. It's bad enough

15:11.218 --> 15:12.418
the girls have
to see me like this.

15:12.452 --> 15:14.320
Not them too.

15:14.354 --> 15:16.021
Okay.

15:16.056 --> 15:17.957
But we're all on your side.

15:20.994 --> 15:22.027
Talk to me.

15:23.964 --> 15:26.132
Everything comes
down to one judge

15:26.166 --> 15:27.733
in one moment

15:27.768 --> 15:29.034
who knows nothing about me,

15:29.069 --> 15:31.537
except that I lost my
temper three years ago.

15:31.571 --> 15:32.772
That's what
the letters are for...

15:32.806 --> 15:34.607
I've messed up
everything in my life.

15:34.641 --> 15:36.642
- That's not true.
- It is true!

15:36.676 --> 15:38.344
It's my fault,

15:38.378 --> 15:39.478
- and I know that.
- Listen to me...

15:39.513 --> 15:40.579
When I read that article

15:40.614 --> 15:41.614
about you and the girls

15:41.648 --> 15:43.315
and the switch,

15:43.350 --> 15:44.517
I knew this was

15:44.551 --> 15:46.252
what I was
supposed to do...

15:46.286 --> 15:48.087
Find you and them

15:48.121 --> 15:50.189
- and make it right.
- Listen to me.

15:50.223 --> 15:53.058
I have a really
good feeling about this,

15:53.093 --> 15:55.761
and you know I'm never
wrong about these things.

15:55.796 --> 15:57.930
- Hmm?
- Guard: No touching.

16:03.069 --> 16:04.003
<i>( Door opens )</i>

16:05.539 --> 16:06.672
- Hi.
- Hey.

16:06.706 --> 16:07.840
Thought I'd grab
some of that duck salad

16:07.874 --> 16:09.809
you made last night.

16:09.843 --> 16:10.810
Mm. Sorry.

16:10.844 --> 16:11.811
I just finished it.

16:11.845 --> 16:12.778
( Chuckles ) That's okay.

16:12.813 --> 16:14.580
I'll get something else.

16:14.614 --> 16:16.649
So, what are you working on?

16:16.683 --> 16:17.716
Thought you were done.

16:17.751 --> 16:19.552
I have a meeting

16:19.586 --> 16:21.353
with the head
of digital marketing.

16:21.388 --> 16:24.223
My editor says we have to "beef
up our online presence,"

16:24.257 --> 16:27.293
so she want me to start a blog.

16:27.327 --> 16:28.427
Really?

16:28.462 --> 16:30.496
Look at you, the blogger.

16:30.530 --> 16:33.365
I have to come up
with some ideas for topics.

16:33.400 --> 16:35.134
Oh!

16:35.168 --> 16:37.136
- Let me get some brussels sprouts.
- Oh, that'd be great.

16:37.204 --> 16:39.872
Yeah. After that, I have
to get out of here, honey.

16:39.906 --> 16:42.041
I have to meet them
in 45 minutes, so...

16:42.075 --> 16:44.844
- Honey, the cable guy's coming.
- He is?

16:44.878 --> 16:46.045
Yeah, from 11:00 to 7:00.
Remember, you told me?

16:46.079 --> 16:47.880
Only reason I remember
is 'cause there's a game

16:47.914 --> 16:49.748
- on tonight.
- Right. Well, I'm sorry. I can't do it.

16:49.783 --> 16:51.951
Um... can you do it?

16:51.985 --> 16:53.853
I have a 2:00 tee time.

16:53.887 --> 16:55.688
Can't you change
your golf time?

16:55.755 --> 16:56.856
It's with the head
of a dealership,

16:56.890 --> 16:58.657
but I've already canceled
on him twice this summer...

16:58.692 --> 17:00.526
Both for book-related events,
I might add.

17:00.560 --> 17:01.594
First was that trip
to New York, and the...

17:01.628 --> 17:02.628
Well, I don't know what to say.

17:02.662 --> 17:03.829
I can't do it, you can't do it.

17:03.864 --> 17:06.332
We'll just have to live
without cable for a while.

17:06.366 --> 17:07.398
There's a game tonight.

17:07.434 --> 17:08.567
I'm sorry about the mess.

17:08.602 --> 17:09.568
( Sighs )

