Go away!

22:01.997 --> 22:04.799
Don't you want to feel my
slippery, slimy, rubbery skin?

22:04.833 --> 22:07.702
You cannot gross me out
because I am a professional.

22:07.736 --> 22:10.104
How can you be a chef
if you're vegetarian?

22:10.139 --> 22:11.873
