22:11.907 --> 22:13.942
( Scoffs ) I don't want to
make out with it, or anything,

22:13.976 --> 22:15.576
but I don't mind
being around it.

22:15.611 --> 22:16.644
It's just a personal choice.

22:16.679 --> 22:17.912
Well, whatever you do,
don't tell chef.

22:17.947 --> 22:20.448
He's got no love
for vegetarians.

22:20.482 --> 22:22.750
Hey, uh, what is he
making with artichokes?

22:22.785 --> 22:24.419
I didn't see that
on the menu tonight.

22:24.453 --> 22:26.321
I don't know,
but I hope we get some.

22:26.355 --> 22:27.322
<i>( Chuckles )</i>

22:29.325 --> 22:30.391
- Chef...
- What are you doing?

22:30.426 --> 22:32.360
Trimming artichokes.
Like you asked.

22:32.394 --> 22:34.896
I said <i>haricots verts.</i>

22:34.930 --> 22:36.264
