Hey, honey!
How'd it go?

27:36.990 --> 27:38.257
What did you make tonight?

27:38.291 --> 27:41.093
Did you boss make
those mussels again?

27:41.128 --> 27:43.029
'Cause I'm dying to try them.

27:44.164 --> 27:45.097
No.

27:47.134 --> 27:48.934
Is everything okay?

27:48.969 --> 27:50.703
Did something happen?

27:50.737 --> 27:52.638
I'm just tired.
I'm gonna go in.

27:52.672 --> 27:54.440
Honey.

27:54.474 --> 27:55.808
If something happened,
you can tell me.

27:55.842 --> 27:56.776
( Curtly ) Nothing happened.

27:58.412 --> 27:59.445
Okay.

28:02.315 --> 28:04.483
Hey, remember that lecture
when, like, 9,000 mosquitoes

28:04.518 --> 28:06.152
were attacking us?

28:06.186 --> 28:08.287
( Weak chuckle ) Yeah.

28:08.321 --> 28:11.090
- That sucked.
- Yeah.

28:14.261 --> 28:15.261
So what do you
want to do this weekend?

28:15.295 --> 28:16.996
<i>( Motorcycle revving )</i>

28:27.007 --> 28:27.940
You all right?

28:30.610 --> 28:31.677
Yeah.

28:35.782 --> 28:37.516
Not really.

28:39.252 --> 28:40.453
Alex, it's...

28:40.487 --> 28:41.487
"It's not you."

28:43.490 --> 28:45.424
That's what you're gonna say.

28:45.459 --> 28:47.226
"It's not you,
it's me."

28:49.196 --> 28:51.097
I am so sorry.

28:51.131 --> 28:53.299
I... I just think
that I'm...

28:53.333 --> 28:55.000
Hung up on someone else.

28:58.772 --> 29:00.139
Yeah, I could tell...

29:00.173 --> 29:02.775
( Sighs ) From your
reaction at the book party.

29:04.744 --> 29:06.679
I don't want to
be hung up on him.

