your head half an inch

30:15.649 --> 30:17.283
while you're talking to me.

30:17.317 --> 30:19.118
World chaos if you learned,
I don't know,

30:19.152 --> 30:21.153
three signs!
Chicken, ribs, crab.

30:21.188 --> 30:22.321
It's not that hard.
That's it!

30:22.355 --> 30:23.355
That's all he has to do!

30:23.390 --> 30:25.291
- Whoa.
- ( Deep sigh )

30:25.325 --> 30:28.093
I'm gonna be stuck
as a dishwasher,

30:28.128 --> 30:30.229
or a truck driver

30:30.263 --> 30:31.297
for the rest of my life.

30:31.331 --> 30:33.132
I really don't think
that you're gonna

30:33.166 --> 30:35.167
end up a truck driver.

30:36.770 --> 30:37.870
You're wrong.

30:37.904 --> 30:39.939
I've seen it.
We get...

30:39.973 --> 30:41.640
Pigeonholed.

