Kathryn, what
are you doing here?

31:25.832 --> 31:28.100
I heard you got fired
or moved to the back.

31:28.134 --> 31:29.167
How did you hear that?

31:29.202 --> 31:30.936
I called my friend.

31:30.970 --> 31:33.739
Honey, they can't demote you
just because you're deaf.

31:33.773 --> 31:34.973
First of all, it's not legal.

31:35.007 --> 31:36.608
Yes, it is.

31:36.642 --> 31:37.909
He thinks I'm unsafe.
He's allowed to find

31:37.944 --> 31:39.578
a different place
for me in the kitchen.

31:39.612 --> 31:40.746
That's just absurd.

31:40.780 --> 31:42.781
- Look, we'll get you an interpreter...
- No.

31:42.815 --> 31:45.550
It's too crowded in there,
they'll get in the way.

31:45.585 --> 31:47.352
I don't want an interpreter.

31:47.387 --> 31:49.154
