- No no no! You can't talk to him!

31:53.393 --> 31:55.293
- Someone has to.
- Kathryn, no!

31:55.328 --> 31:57.028
Is there a problem here?

31:57.063 --> 32:00.298
- Well, actually...
- No, chef. No problem.

32:00.333 --> 32:02.000
You sure?

32:02.034 --> 32:03.168
We're fine.

32:07.907 --> 32:09.040
Kathryn, if you say anything,

32:09.075 --> 32:10.809
I swear I will
never forgive you.

32:10.843 --> 32:11.810
Daphne.

32:11.844 --> 32:13.578
I mean it.
Go home, please!

32:15.815 --> 32:18.750
- ( Laughs )
- I am 42 years old and I am still

32:18.785 --> 32:20.685
