Try to hide these
behind like, you know,

32:24.457 --> 32:25.524
- five packs of gum.
- ( Chuckles )

32:26.559 --> 32:28.226
Wow.
You're sure hurrying

32:28.261 --> 32:29.394
things along, aren't you?

32:29.429 --> 32:32.431
I told Daphne I'd be home by
10:00 to read over her papers.

32:32.465 --> 32:34.399
Well, chop-chop.

32:34.434 --> 32:35.434
You know, in a couple years

32:35.468 --> 32:37.202
I won't have Daphne
at home anymore,

32:37.236 --> 32:39.971
