more time...

32:40.006 --> 32:41.239
You know, if we're
still together by then.

32:41.274 --> 32:44.776
- I certainly hope we are.
- You do?

32:44.811 --> 32:46.812
Yeah. I may not
believe in marriage,

32:46.846 --> 32:48.747
