36:56.239 --> 36:57.506
What she didn't tell you is

36:57.541 --> 36:59.408
I banned her from
going to games

36:59.443 --> 37:00.509
for the rest of the season.

37:00.544 --> 37:02.445
( Laughing )

37:08.051 --> 37:09.151
What are you gonna do?

37:09.186 --> 37:11.020
( Deep sigh )

37:11.054 --> 37:12.855
I guess go back

37:12.889 --> 37:15.858
and try to get
a system like you said,

37:15.892 --> 37:17.927
make him realize
I'm worth the extra effort.

37:19.696 --> 37:20.629
You are.

37:26.570 --> 37:27.570
You are.

37:39.082 --> 37:41.050
I put up a mirror.

37:41.084 --> 37:42.384
I can see that.

37:42.419 --> 37:44.019
Is it okay?

37:46.857 --> 37:48.824
It's okay.

37:59.936 --> 38:01.837
( Footsteps approach )

38:02.906 --> 38:04.740
<i>( Knocks on door )</i>

38:04.774 --> 38:05.741
Can I come in?

38:05.775 --> 38:07.743
Sure.

38:07.777 --> 38:10.412
