your papers, counselors.</i>

38:47.884 --> 38:49.585
Do you have anything
to add before

38:49.619 --> 38:52.688
I make my ruling on
Mr. Sorrento's removability?

38:52.722 --> 38:54.657
Government lawyer: Only that
Mr. Sorrento came to this country

38:54.691 --> 38:57.426
to avoid prosecution
for an aggravated assault...

38:57.460 --> 38:59.361
That's in your papers.

38:59.396 --> 39:00.462
Mr. Mullavey,
anything new?

39:00.497 --> 39:03.098
I would only stress
that removing my client

39:03.133 --> 39:05.067
would unfairly separate him
from the daughter he only

39:05.101 --> 39:06.035
recently discovered...

39:06.069 --> 39:08.304
That's in your papers.

39:08.338 --> 39:10.906
I got it.
Mr. Sorrento.

39:10.941 --> 39:12.908
<i>The criminal charges</i>
<i>against you in Italy</i>

39:12.943 --> 39:15.778
were reduced
and you paid a fine. Yes?

39:15.812 --> 39:18.080
- Yes, your honor.
- <i>So you are no longer a wanted man.</i>

39:18.114 --> 39:19.882
<i>That's good.</i>

39:19.916 --> 39:23.652
And the unique circumstances
of your daughters...

39:23.687 --> 39:26.822
Uh, should I say
both your daughters...

39:26.856 --> 39:28.824
<i>Are compelling,</i>
<i>to say the least.</i>

39:28.858 --> 39:30.559
<i>But while compelling,</i>

39:30.594 --> 39:33.495
those circumstances don't
rise to the level of hardship

39:33.530 --> 39:35.531
if you were to be removed.

39:36.733 --> 39:38.601
<i>You haven't been a presence</i>

39:38.635 --> 39:40.569
<i>in the girls' lives</i>
<i>until now and they have</i>

39:40.604 --> 39:42.504
three other parents.

39:44.374 --> 39:45.474
Moreover,

39:45.508 --> 39:48.210
this court is troubled

39:48.244 --> 39:50.980
<i>by your overstaying</i>
<i>the initial visa</i>

39:51.014 --> 39:52.147
<i>by several years</i>

39:52.182 --> 39:54.283
before your latest attempt
to enter the country.

39:54.317 --> 39:55.317
