the initial law he broke

40:00.256 --> 40:01.957
by overstaying his visa.

40:01.992 --> 40:04.026
<i>And while the Italian court</i>

40:04.060 --> 40:05.761
reduced his charges,

40:05.795 --> 40:07.796
it didn't absolve
him completely.

40:07.831 --> 40:11.700
This court can't ignore the
pattern of law-breaking.

40:11.735 --> 40:13.569
For this reason,

40:13.603 --> 40:16.672
I grant the government's
petition for removal

40:16.706 --> 40:20.442
and order Mr. Sorrento
return to Italy.

40:20.477 --> 40:22.478
