40:22.512 --> 40:23.512
What just happened?

40:23.546 --> 40:24.647
I'm so sorry, Bay.

40:24.681 --> 40:26.448
<i>The detainee will be taken back</i>

40:26.483 --> 40:27.549
into custody

40:27.584 --> 40:29.251
<i>and he'll be placed on a plane</i>

40:29.285 --> 40:30.486
back to his country of origin

40:30.520 --> 40:32.187
within 48 hours.

40:36.192 --> 40:37.159
I'm sorry.

40:40.030 --> 40:41.997
( Sobbing )

40:43.166 --> 40:44.133
I'll go.

40:49.139 --> 40:51.006
Bay, stop!

40:51.041 --> 40:52.875
