some kind of appeal.

40:52.909 --> 40:55.110
I'm sorry.
There's not.

40:55.145 --> 40:56.178
It's not fair.

40:58.148 --> 40:59.882
I just met him

40:59.916 --> 41:02.017
and now they're taking
him away from me.

41:03.620 --> 41:05.020
He's never gonna
be at my graduation.

41:05.055 --> 41:06.689
He's never gonna be
at my wedding.

41:07.891 --> 41:10.392
I feel like I'm never
gonna see him again.

41:10.427 --> 41:12.428
You can... you can
text and Skype,

41:12.462 --> 41:13.562
( stammers )
And you can visit him.

41:13.596 --> 41:14.697
I will take you.

41:17.467 --> 41:19.568
I just thought that we had
some kind of future together...

41:19.602 --> 41:23.138
You and me and him.

41:24.407 --> 41:25.607
It's so childish.

41:27.410 --> 41:29.378
I'm so sorry.

41:29.412 --> 41:30.412
I know it's not your fault.

41:30.447 --> 41:32.181
I know everyone did
everything they could.

41:32.215 --> 41:33.515
